text: haey brasenbae puokke( puok poutatbot) ban berchenh vinh noh chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha a l laoh temuoyokt ku krob krean samreab khnhom . kmean mcheasa na del trauv ke korp sakkar da pit brakd krawpi trong laey . champoh trong temuoyokt del khnhom ban brakl kar touk chetd haey trong kuchea mcheasa nei a r sh da thomtheng
